testcase.name: Creating a Time should throw an IllegalArgumentException for hours not within 0 and 23
Creating a Time should throw an IllegalArgumentException for minutes not within 0 and 59
The default arguments for hours and minutes should be equal to 0
Calling minus or - should return the correct difference in minutes
Calling toString should return a properly formatted string representation
Calling Ordered operators should work as expected
